quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,44,"Alla homo waylita jemma on e √Īalawma on, pellet, na wonii e …óum tasakuyee wonan'de joomiraa…ďe jii…óe …ďen."
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala kullel immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muu…óum, no e majji yaarooji koy…óe muu…óm no e majji kadi yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi. Alla homo Taga ko o muuyi, pellet, Alla ko kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  24,46,"GooŇč…óii Min njippinii Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe, Alla no feewna on mo O muuyii fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  24,47,"He…ďe mbia: "Min gooŇč…óinii Alla e Nulaa…óo on, min …óoftike, refti huccita fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďaawo …óuum, …ďen wonaani gooŇč…óin…ďe"."
  24,48,"Si …ďe noddaama fa'ade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, tawa fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe."
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kam…ďe mari goonga ka, …ďe ngara e makko ko …ďe …óoftii…ďe."
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, kaa …ďe sikkiti, kaa …ďe hulu wota Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on too√Īu …ďe? Ko woni, …ďee ko kam…ďe woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol goo…óin…ďe …ďen si …ďe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ko nde …ďe mbi'ata: "Min nanii men …óoftike." ∆Āen …óon ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďen."
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e nulaa…óo makko on o kuli Alla o rentii [e Lepte makko …óen] haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe ngoni malaa…ďe …ďen."
  24,53,"∆Āe ngoo…óndiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ď…ďe, si a yamirii …ďe ma …ďe njaltu sanne. Maaku: "wota on ngoo…óndu, …óoftaare no nganndaa, pellet, Alla ko kumpitii…óo ko ngolloton""